programme.title: Why We Hunt
programme.desc:
We are back with Season 9 of GWGTV! Join us for our first episode:
Why We Hunt with Jen O'Hara, Norissa Harman, and Kristy Titus.
Hunters are often asked the question, "Why do you hunt?".
The answer to this question is uniquely personal to every hunter and often begins with how we started hunting.
